parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated
airbags deploy inadvertently
airbags do not deploy in a crash
cracked dashboard around airbag area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in remedying the airbag recall can lead to injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Received recall notice but no remedy available
dealer unable to repair due to parts unavailability
manufacturer exceeding reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the dashboard around the airbag area can lead to injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Cracking of the dashboard around the airbag area
cracked dashboard causing concern for airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard can cause sharp pieces of plastic to become projectiles in the event of an accident, potentially causing injuries to occupants. Additionally, the cracking can lead to rattling and loose dashboard components, which can be a distraction to the driver.
symptoms: The dashboard has cracks
especially around the airbag and instrument panel areas
which can lead to rattling and loose dashboard components. In some cases
the cracks can cause shards of plastic to fall into the dashboard and become projectiles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard can cause sharp edges, which can lead to injuries, and potentially affect the deployment of airbags, causing further harm to occupants.
symptoms: Cracks on the dashboard
often near the airbag locations
which can spread over time
and in some cases
cause sharp plastic pieces to fall onto the floor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of door handles can cause injuries, as the chrome plating can peel off and become razor-sharp, and in the event of an accident, can make it difficult for occupants to exit the vehicle or for emergency responders to access the vehicle.
symptoms: Door handles breaking or becoming loose
causing injuries
and in some cases
making it difficult to open the doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the frame can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Rusting of the frame
particularly in areas with high humidity or salt usage on roads.
